data.description: Welcome to this private home built in 2020 with open floor plan, 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths and 1 half bath all within walking distance to Fairyland Elementary and the soccer fields.  Enjoy being surrounded by woods and privacy.  The home has a 2 car garage, office on the main floor, laundry room, playroom and finished bonus room over the garage (could be another bedroom).  The welcoming front porch is wonderful place to relax or enjoy the screened in back porch.  The large kitchen has granite countertops, vented hood over stove, lots of cabinets.  Come see this fabulous family home!
